            "text": "<p>Inspired by the Japanese philosophy of Oubaitori — “each person is a unique individual with their own beauty” — 82X believes that true beauty comes from the balance between appearance, health, and inner strength. This philosophy aligns with the growing wellness movement in the U.S, where consumers increasingly prioritize holistic, inside-out beauty solutions.</p><p>To meet these expectations, 82X invests in advanced R&D with a dedicated laboratory in Japan, led by experts with over 20 years of experience in beauty and health. By combining premium natural ingredients with cutting-edge Japanese technology, 82X enhances absorption and effectiveness - delivering visible results.</p><p> More than just a supplement, 82X Collagen & Placenta offers a comprehensive beauty solution designed for modern women in the U.S who seek safe, effective, and long-term wellness from within. Beyond skincare, 82X represents a lifestyle, empowering women to feel confident, radiant, and in control of their beauty journey, while redefining premium Japanese standards in the global wellness market.<br/><br/></p>"
